  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/3032",
  "title": "Add options to disable COUNT on menuSelect widget",
  "body": "The menuSelect widget does not have any way to disable the COUNT. \r\nThere is no CSS selector to hide it or any parameter to enable or disable it when adding the widget. \r\n\r\nThis is what gets render:\r\n\r\n`<option value=\"Arriendo\" class=\"ais-menu-select--option\"><div>Arriendo (354)</div></option>`\r\n\r\nit will be nice to have it like this:\r\n\r\n``<option value=\"Arriendo\" class=\"ais-menu-select--option\"><div>Arriendo <span class=\"ais-menu--count\"> (354)</span></div></option>``",
